Name: Absinthia's Bottled Spirits
Description:
Absinthia's Bottled Spirits is a WBENC-Certified women-owned company based in California. Their products are created by a mixologist and an absintheure and are made with all-natural ingredients. They are used by bartenders and consumers to easily make artisanal, unique, and bold cocktails. 

They currently have seven award-winning products - Blanche, Verte, and Barrel-Aged Absinthe, and four craft syrups Caged Heat, Crimson Smoke, Fairy Dust, and Cherry Bomb. Their carefully crafted, small batch, farm to glass absinthe is delicious with ice and cool water and in hundreds of cocktails such as the Sazerac, Corpse Reviver, and Death in the Afternoon. Their syrups are used to easily make artisanal, unique, and bold cocktails and mocktails.
Product_Types:
Absinthe

Name: AgriTech Corp.
Description: SoilKit is a soil health technology platform starting with a lab-based soil test and finishing with an annual program. The SoilKit Agronomy Cloud collects soils and other data to improve crop production, reduce pollution, and increase carbon sequestration. The current technology offers consumers, hobby farmers, and landscape businesses easy access to laboratory soil testing. These constituents benefit from improved outcomes and lower costs. By leveraging its army of citizen scientists, SoilKit offers ESG opportunities to municipalities, landscape companies, and retailers by improving soil health and increasing soil organic carbon through its recommendations.

Description:
Aigner Chocolates is one of the oldest chocolate shops in New York City, making and purveying handcrafted confections in Forest Hills, Queens since 1930.

What started as Krause’s Candy Kitchen in 1930 has become a neighborhood institution and cornerstone of the Forest
Hills community. The Aigner family took over from the Krause’s in the early 1960s, making chocolate and candy
confections for three generations. In 2015, husband and wife duo Mark Libertini and Rachel Kellner became the new owners, continuing traditions and beginning many of their own.

All of Aigner’s chocolate is produced on-site using antique equipment and recipes that have been passed down through the
generations, including the traditional Austrian/German confections for which Aigner Chocolates is known.
Product_Types: Assorted Gift Boxes, Caramels, Marzipan, Nonpareils
Where:

Anar Gourmet Foods (AGF) crafts all natural, gluten-free seasoning kits for authentic & fusion Indian food with South Indian family recipes. It's perfect for foodies who are intimidated to cook Indian food at home. Delighted customers online and in local Pittsburgh stores such as Whole Foods and Market Districts have given Anar Gourmet Foods all 5-star reviews due to the following attributes:

* All natural ingredients w/no gluten, MSG, soy, sugar, nuts or preservatives.

* Family sized portions.

Name: Anne Cate
Description:
Anne Cate is a Made in America accessories brand and manufacturer specializing in skyline silhouette purses and other simple accessories. Founded in 2016, the Anne Cate skyline collection, which now features over 100 hand-designed skylines, animates your adventures of cities around the world. 
 
They proudly sew every Anne Cate product themselves at their manufacturing studio in Cleveland, Ohio. Quality and community are most important, which is why each product is created using locally and domestically sourced, high quality materials. At Anne Cate, they strive to craft simple and affordable accessories of high quality and value that hold meaning for each customer.
 
Their products are more than just a purse or a pillow; they tell a story that is unique to each person. Whether it is a place we visit, a place we leave, or a place we come home to, your story is captured with an Anne Cate. Finding a meaningful gift for the person who has everything has never been easier - It’s an Anne Cate!
Product_Types:
Clutches & Bags
Throw Pillow
RPO: Women's Business Enterprise Council Ohio River Valley (WBEC ORV)

Product_Types:
The Dipe n' Wipe, is a full diaper kit that is slim enough to fit in your pocket, always ready for use and becomes odor free! The kit includes 1 quality diaper, 5 large & thick wipes and the bag is reusable or recyclable however you need to use it. 

The Magic Wipe, is a small disc that magically expands into a full wet wipe within 10 seconds after pressing the center. It's easy to fit in your wallet and safe to use for your face, body or baby butts. It's a signature wipe to carry on the daily for parents and all people.

Description:
Bake Me Healthy is a purpose-driven, healthy baking M/WBENC small business. We make it easy to bake with natural and organic plant-based ingredients, less sugar and artificial-free food coloring. We offer baking kits featuring natural and organic plant-based ingredients from small businesses that are women-owned, minority-owned and/or focused on sustainability. Our bakes are delicious, nutritious and cater to dietary restrictions such as gluten-free and vegan.  They are also kid-tested and mom-approved. 

Plus, a portion of our proceeds are invested in Hot Bread Kitchen, a non-profit that empowers women to obtain jobs in the culinary industry. Not only do families learn about baking healthy, but they also learn the importance of supporting small businesses. It's a fun feel good, bake good, taste good family experience.

Name: Bake Me Healthy
Description: Bake Me Healthy is a women and Asian-owned healthy baking business on a mission to help others bake better for themselves, their families, and the planet without compromising health, taste, or the planet. It was founded by Kimberle Lau, a former beauty executive, who developed lactose and egg intolerances from pregnancy and then had to eliminate soy from her diet due to becoming high-risk for breast cancer. Bake Me Healthy offers convenient, delicious baking mixes that are Top 9 Allergen-Free, plant-based, refined sugar-free, and upcycled.

Bessie's signature monster-style cookie was invented when owner Jen was struggling with her milk supply but sick of the typical cardboard-flavored lactation cookies. Description:
As seen on Shark Tank, Bug Bite Thing is a chemical-free solution that instantly alleviates the itching, stinging, and swelling from bug bites and stings. This FDA registered, class 1 medical device uses suction to remove the saliva/venom left underneath the skin. Unlike topical creams and ointments, the problem is eliminated, not masked. It works on mosquitoes, bees, wasps, ants, biting flies, splinters & other biting insects. 

Amazon’s #1 selling product for insect bite relief with over 60,000 reviews is reusable and safe to use on all ages. 

Founder and CEO, Kelley Higney, discovered the tool to help her own daughter who suffered terribly from bug bites. Now she is a “Mom on a Mission” to educate the world on the most effective, chemical-free solution for insect bite relief.

Description: Bump Health exists to fight on behalf of Moms and their families by bringing trust into every aspect of their parenting journey. We’re a women’s health brand that serves moms before, during, and after pregnancy. And we’re driven by the idea of a world that treats moms the way each of us treats our own.
Product_Types:
We currently have four business units offering products:

Bump Consumer — We own a portfolio of direct-to-consumer ecommerce brands, including Bump Boxes, Bitsy Boxes, Glow Organics, and more.

Bump Medical — Expecting moms are entitled to thousands of dollars of free products from their health insurance providers. We get mom everything she’s owed, with no out-of-pocket cost.

Bump Wellness — Wellness perks for 300+ corporate clients. Fully customized boxes for maternity, new hires, remote workers, and more. For companies like GrubHub, Walgreens, and American Eagle

Bump Life — Our newest business that’s currently being incubated. Life insurance for new moms and their babies.

Name: Capuli Edible Fruit Teas
Description:
Capuli offers whole fruit teas naturally sweetened with imperfect fruits. Their signature blends of herbs, fruits, and spices open the door to a whole new world of flavor and health benefits. They are simple, healthy, sustainable, and beautiful. Just rehydrate, invigorate, and enjoy!

They craft their packs in Redmond, WA and source local fruits — apples, cherries, peaches, pears, and strawberries from small local farmers. They strive to use what farmers call "seconds" or the misshapen or really rips fruits.

Velvet Hibiscus Whole Fruit Tea
Zesty Cherry Whole Fruit Tea
Sampler Gift Box
Fruit Tea Gift Box

Name: Caskata
Description:
Caskata Artisanal Home creates dinnerware rooted in the practical, the useful, and the things to treasure forever. The unique blend of classic and contemporary pieces are easy to mix and match, and make it simple to set a table you love.

One of only a handful of ateliers of its kind in this country, the artisans and designers at Caskata create beautiful handmade bone china and porcelain tableware that's delicate to look at, but strong enough to use every day. In their skylit studios they combine inspiration drawn from the New England landscapes and coastlines that surround their workshop, with perspectives formed by years spent in New York and Paris. With a focus on contemporary interpretations of classic motifs, their compositions are both timeless and fresh. Meticulous attention to detail is evidenced in each handmade piece, making these true modern-day heirlooms.
Product_Types:
Dinnerware
Platters & Serveware
Glassware
Dinner Napkins

Description: CheerNotes is a stationery brand, retailer, and distributor of inclusive designs from over 35 diverse creatives. Almost 90% of our Artist Partners are women of color and their work reflects their cultural identity and other life experiences - from cards in Spanish to celebrating sobriety anniversaries. Our collection has 300+ cards and we've worked with multiple organizations to create custom stationery. We’re also expanding to other stationery! CheerNotes is a connection company, not a holiday company. We help people connect with the products they buy, the creatives who made them, the person they gift to, and themselves through self-expression.

Description:
In 2015, Canadian Linda Peers recognized an unmet need for a traditionally fermented kefir that was plant-based, organic and 100% additive-free. As a result, she formulated a dairy-free coconut milk kefir, called The Cultured Coconut, which is now available in over 1,500 stores across Canada.  
This innovative natural food that contributes to healthy gut flora provides an exceptionally high probiotic value of live and active bacteria. Just one daily tablespoon provides over 4 trillion Colony Forming Units (CFU) and over 40 probiotic strains. Safe for babies, children of all ages, pregnant and nursing women, as well as pets.
Product_Types: The Cultured Coconut - fermented organic coconut milk kefir

Description: Here at Love + Chew, we’re passionate about making plant-based eating easy on the go. Our cookies are beautifully and simplistically packaged, and our main ingredients are almonds, dates, and chia seeds. We’re a female-owned San Francisco-based company and we believe that the plant-based lifestyle is not just for vegans but can be integrated into anyone’s lifestyle. Our recipes are inspired by our founder’s family’s recipes and lifestyle, which are made with whole food ingredients. Our customers love our cookies as a quick breakfast chopped up over yogurt, or a healthier afternoon snack to beat those 3 pm hangries

Description:
CONQUERing is a global jewelry brand on a mission to help people feel empowered with interchangeable fidget jewelry. They’re driven to create products that help their customers feel calm, focused and inspired so they can live with intention to “conquer their day.” 

CONQUERing is committed to inclusivity — they offer the largest size range of any jewelry brand, offer products for those with different abilities, bring awareness to sensitive topics and support marginalized groups. CONQUERing donates 5% of its profits to charitable organizations that share their passion for empowering others.

Interchangeable Jewelry
Jewelry Gift Sets

Jacqueline Jones created Crystal Eikcaj™ Skin and Hair Care to help resolve many of the health issues she experienced over the years.  (Alopecia, acute arthritis, severe dry skin and diabetes).

Description: At Cultivate Taste we don't use flavorings, candy, or sugar in our teas. Feel good knowing that a certified tea specialist from the Specialty Tea Institute has sourced direct, blends, and sells international award winning handcrafted and single origin loose-leaf teas online, our tea salon, and wholesale. We strive to source organic and fair-trade teas directly from farms across China, Japan, Sri Lanka, Thailand, Taiwan, India, etc… We blend using premium organic and fair-trade ingredients to enhance a tea not to mask it because we want you to enjoy and develop your palate, while feeling good that you're drinking something healthy too.

Name: Cultured Kombucha Co.
Description:
Cultured Kombucha Co. was founded in 2015 as the first microbrewery of kombucha tea in Northern Michigan. Their tart, sweet and bubbly tea creates a probiotic health beverage focused on nourishing your body from the inside out. Cultured kombucha is certified organic, certified vegan, and certified women owned. Their unique kombucha flavors are minimally processed to bring you the most pure kombucha possible. For more information, please visit
www.drinkcultured.com or follow on Facebook at @CulturedKombucha.
Product_Types: Cultured Kombucha Co. Kombucha Tea

Name: Daddy's Homemade, LLC
Description: Amber, a mother of three and proud small business owner, never expected that creating homemade syrup for family breakfast would become Daddy’s Homemade All-Natural Syrup. Inspired by a family health journey to eliminate high fructose corn syrup and artificial ingredients from the store bought syrup they used, the venture grew from a kitchen experiment to a heartfelt mission. Inspired by the eldest daughter's hand-drawn logo of the three kids, the syrups offer more than just breakfast delight; they enhance coffee, cocktails, cooking and more. They are even produced in sustainable packaging to help the environment.
Product_Types: All natural syrup used to elevate breakfast; food and beverages. Available in various flavors and in 4 sizes.
Where: Blossoming Boutique; Fun and Funky Art Galleries and Gifts; Moore Lumber/Ace Hardware in Pine Junction, Aspen Park and Evergreen; The Ranchers Wife; A Borgata; The Perfect Gift Colorado Artisans in Colorado Mills; Lynn's Whistle Shop; 12th Ave Market; All the Good Stuff

Name: Daily Crunch Snacks
Description:
Daily Crunch is a women-owned & mission-driven company that makes Uniquely Crunchy™ sprouted nut snacks that taste as good as they make you feel.  With a process and commitment to clean ingredients, Daily Crunch transforms ordinary nuts into Uniquely Crunchy™, easier to digest, more nutrient-dense nut snacks.

Cherry Berry Sprouted Nut Medley: Ditch your old trail mix for the berry best sprouted nut mix. Our Cherry Berry Sprouted Nut Medley contains a Uniquely Crunchy™ mix of sprouted almonds, walnuts and cashews paired with antioxidant-rich dried cherries and blueberries. This sprouted nut snack is clean and packed with protein.

Nashville Hot Sprouted Almonds: This vegan take on the iconic “Nashville Hot” flavor is an ode to Daily Crunch’s hometown, where spicy hot chicken reigns. Natural monk fruit sweetener balances out the fiery spice of paprika and cayenne, resulting in a flavor-packed bite every time. Medium-heat and Uniquely Crunchy™, this sprouted nut snack is clean + packed with protein.
Product_Types:
Uniquely Crunchy™ sprouted nut snacks 
- Cherry Berry Sprouted Nut Medley
- Nashville Hot Sprouted Almonds
Where: Meijer, CVS, Erewhon, Kings, Raleys, Hy-Vee

Description:
Daybird is an anti-beauty brand creating clean, vegan functional makeup for a one-step morning routine, giving back people's time and mental space to do what matters most. Daybird’s mission is to redefine beauty standards so that there is no standard, and people have taken back ownership of what beauty means and looks like in their lives.

Daybird was founded by two female founders of color, Whitney McElwain and Veena Krishnan.
Product_Types:
Tinted Skincare is a one-step morning routine that combines two active serums, moisturizer, mineral sunscreen, and sheer tint. 

Tinted Skincare is non-comedogenic and dermatologist approved, with niacinamide at 2% and bisabolol (chamomile extract) at 0.5%, levels that are clinically proven to deliver the benefits of each ingredient.

Dress It Up Dressing is a line of award-winning, premium salad dressings made with clean, nutritious ingredients to meet the demands of today’s consumers. 

In a category known for taking shortcuts and making compromises, Dress It Up offers dressings as healthy as home-made for the customer who reads labels and seeks mouth-watering flavor. Their delicious blends of olive-oil based dressings can instantly transform the humblest greens into a gourmet meal. Dress It Up Dressing is a certified B-Corp.

Name: Emily Phillips

Emily Phillips is a Nashville-based collection of women's shirts and shirtdresses ethically made in the USA with natural and sustainable fabrics and practices. Name: Envio® Skincare — Smart Skin Health, LLC
Description:
Envio® offers clinically proven plant-based products for issue-prone skin, as well as education and counseling services to support the emotional hurdles that may come with skin concerns. Their current customer focus is on Millennials and Gen Z!  
 
Envio founders Jan & Carol are a mother-daughter duo filling a gap in the market with the first digitally native regimen that is double the strength of any existing DTC acne subscription kits, as well as licensed online mental health counseling through Betterhelp.com. They deliver directly to your door, no appointment necessary, with a 60-Day money-back guarantee.
  
The brand looks to help acne sufferers to see themselves clearly again™.
Product_Types:
BPO 5% Cleanser
SA 2% Gel Serum
Gel Hydrator
Clarifying Clay Mask

Name: FIT2order, LLC
Description: FIT2order provides wellness solutions for our sedentary workforce, including our band2FIT strength training programs for Travel (Total Body and Core), Posture Correction, Seniors, Kids and Cancer Survivors. Each signature program is imprinted ON the band and the exercises can be performed in small spaces, such as workstations and hotel rooms.
Product_Types:
Health and Wellbeing products to move MORE and stress LESS AT WORK 
1. The vidaBALL® is a handheld device designed to help you manage daily stress using guided breath techniques. This easy-to-use tool will guide you to the present moment using a simple combination of light and vibrational feedback.
2. Signature Resistance Bands- FIT2order's resistance bands feature signature programs imprinted ON the band. A convenient strength training tool for Posture Correction, Long Distance Travel, Healthy Back, Total Body and Core Strength, Seniors, Kids, and Cancer Recovery. 
3. With the Healthy @WORK Employee Kit, your desk-bound employees will have the tools needed to create small, healthy habits while working that will lead to larger lifestyle changes.

Description:
Forté Chocolate was born when our founder Karen Neugebauer moved near the historic Skagit Valley, a region known for its distinctive farm-raised flavors and Pacific Northwest artisan culture. There she found a tightknit community and loyal following for her exceptionally tasty and beautiful chocolate confections. Next thing you know, Chef Karen was winning national and international awards, and bringing her passion for craft and cunningly balanced flavor profiles to the highest echelons of the chocolate world as one of its best chocolatiers.

Today at her production kitchen, near the flagship boutique in downtown Mt. Vernon, a seasoned team of artisan chocolatiers embody an creative mindset, carefully crafting every chocolate by hand in limited quantities, using traditional techniques of tempering, pouring, enrobing, and adding the finishing touches to each truffle, caramel and specialty bar. All handcrafted for the love of taste and beauty, they invite you to imagine your greatest chocolate desires at one of their boutique chocolateries, online, or by custom order.
Product_Types:
Signature Truffles
Sea Salt Caramels
Chocolate Bars
Barks & Everyday Favorites

Description:
Fresh Monster was born out of the belief that there shouldn’t be so many tradeoffs when it comes to keeping kids clean. 

Natural products should work just as well as regular products. Safe products  should be affordable. Kids products should be made just for kids, not borrowed from babies or adults. 

That’s why Fresh Monster was created by two moms on a mission to clean up the personal care aisle. 

Fresh Monster is affordable, natural, hair and body care designed and formulated just for kids.

Shampoo
Bodywash
Deodorant
Hair Gel

Description:
Goldbug is a leader in the infant and young children’s accessory market. Goldbug leads through innovative design, safety and quality expertise, strong execution and long-standing partnerships. The company’s products include infant and young children’s socks, shoes, slippers hair accessories, jewelry and sunglasses as well as travel products that include car mirrors, head supports, safety harnesses, diaper bags, soft toys and more.  

Goldbug has established philanthropic initiatives that include investments locally and nationally to improve maternal health in the United States.  Details about this work are included on the company’s website at:  https://goldbuginc.com/blog/

Name: Good & Tasty Bakes
Description:
At Good & Tasty Bakes, our focus is on producing the highest-quality and freshest desserts possible. Our desserts feature all-natural ingredients including locally-produced butter and pure 100% rBGH-free cream cheese from dairies and farms throughout the western United States. You will never find high fructose corn syrup, partially hydrogenated oils, artificial flavors, or refined sugar or flour in our cheesecakes!

Our well-trained and experienced bakers start our products from scratch and proudly hand-make each dessert in small batches. Even though this is a more expensive way of producing our products, we feel the exceptional taste, quality, and appearance are worth the extra cost.

Good & Tasty Bakes products are also certified gluten-free through the Gluten-Free Certification Organization. So go on and indulge in one of our Good & Tasty treats, because you deserve it! With these cheesecakes, you can have your sweets and eat them, too!
Product_Types:
Classic Cheesecake
Chocolate Cheesecake
Key Lime Cheesecake
Pumpkin Cheesecake

Name: Green Garmento
Description:
As seen on Shark Tank, say NO to single-use plastic and GREEN your dry-cleaning routine with The Green Garmento 4-in-1 reusable garment bag. 
At home it serves as a space-saving hanging hamper, on your trip to the dry cleaner it morphs into a snazzy carry- bag, and at pick-up, your dry-cleaned clothes will be hanging and protected inside a roomy garment bag - and not a single-use piece of plastic in sight! 

Found in 27 countries, the Green Garmento offers a myriad of reusable bags for dry cleaning, laundry, hospitality, promotions and more. Corporate orders are welcome with custom printing and bulk pricing available.

Reusable Garment Bag
Reusbale Tote

Name: Green Goo
Description:
Green Goo makes potent, portable first aid and body care products. Green Goo makes potent, portable first aid and body care products. They use only plant-based ingredients and slow infuse them in enriching oils. The result is one of the most effective, all-natural product lines on the market.

Green Goo uses time-honored traditions and plant-based ingredients to create a line of body care products that are gentle, effective, cruelty-free, and sustainably sourced. Name: Greentop Gifts
Description:
Greentop Gifts provides multicultural celebration décor, apparel, gifts and gifting supplies. Clarence Claus and Celebration Crew characters have quickly cemented Greentop Gift’s place in African American and families of color households who look for representation during birthday and holiday moments. 

Greentop Gifts was founded in 2016 after founder and CEO, and mom, Jacquelyn Rodgers couldn’t find diverse wrapping paper to wrap gifts for her son. Since its launch, Greentop Gifts has received notable media attention from numerous outlets, including Essence, O, The Oprah Magazine, Good Housekeeping, and People.
Product_Types:
Gift Wrap
Gift Bags
Apparel & Gifts

Description:
Happi Hippo Plant Organics is a sustainable, family-friendly, toxin-free, vegan body care company started in 2020 by a Dentist, Dr. Ann Nguyen-Chung. The brand is plastic-free, certified cruelty-free, and a portion is donated towards humanitarian, animal-welfare, and environmental causes. 

Products include toothpaste tablets, biodegradable vegan floss, bamboo toothbrushes, lip balms, lotion bars, body butters, body scrubs, and bath salts. Our packaging is biodegradable. The skincare products are hand-crafted in small batches right inside the founder's kitchen!

Our tagline is "Eco clean plant-based body care, for a happi you and a happi planet!"

Lip Balms
Solid Lotion Bars

Description:
Herbal Goodness is the #1 manufacturer of premium quality, unique, organic, non-GMO superfoods and herbal products to support healthy living and impact lives. As a 100% women-owned company, they believe in business for social good. They donate 10% of profits to promote the education of African girls in Science and Technology through the WAAW Foundation. 

Their strong background in software engineering enables them to employ cutting-edge technologies to significantly improve operational efficiencies, and pass the savings on to customers. All products are manufactured in the USA, operations are inspected by the Food and Drug Administration, and undergo annual USDA organic certification. 

They support organic farming and empower farmers and their communities through fair trade practices. Through giving, they increase the availability of chemical-free, organic food. Herbal Goodness is green, cares about the environment and uses recycled materials where available.
Product_Types:
Teas
Liquid Extracts
Capsules
Super Greens
Where: Online at HerbalGoodnessCo.com, Amazon.com and Walmart.com

Description:
In 2007, Karen Hertz was diagnosed with thyroid cancer and an autoimmune thyroid disease. After surgery and radiation treatments, her doctors recommended she adopt a gluten-free diet to help with inflammation and recovery. 

As a beer lover, Hertz was devastated at having to cut gluten from her diet. She made it her mission to create world-class gluten-free beer, and thus the idea for Holidaily Brewing Company was born. Holidaily is the largest gluten-free brewery in the USA and the only gluten-free brewery that is certified woman-owned.

Homefree makes ready-to-eat, shelf stable, vegan, whole grain cookies free of gluten and common food allergens including peanuts, tree nuts, eggs and dairy. Description: Finally - the real deal and tart! No Added Sugar, Juice Concentrate, Flavoring, Oil, Fiber, Glycerin, Sucralose, or Sulfur. Honestly Cranberry's Ingredients: Cranberries. AIP, Diabetic, Keto, Paleo, and Whole30 friendly. 15 calories, 4g of carbs and 1g of sugar per serving. 25x the health benefit, per unit weight, when compared to sweetened dried cranberries. Cranberries compliment many flavors and recipes - including cookies, salads, brownies, dips, oatmeal, sauces, breads, pancakes, seafood, burgers, vegetables, and cocktails. Soak them in orange juice before putting them in a bread or cookie, let them soak in salad dressing for a few minutes before adding to the greens, or muddle them in an Old Fashioned cocktail!

Name: House of Kajaana, Inc.
Description:
We believe that the freezer is the treasure chest of the home and House of Kajaana is the crown jewel you’ve been waiting for. House of Kajaana is a delicious, 100% plant-based Indian food company dedicated to bringing the joy of healthy meals to the modern palate. Our First Collection is inspired by some of the beloved Indian classic dishes you know and love: Cauliflower Tikka Masala, Roasted Butternut Saag, and Coconut Malabar Curry. Our high-fiber meals contain 9gs of plant-based protein, are made of whole non-GMO ingredients, free from nuts, gluten, dairy, soy, artificial flavors, and gums, and are served in recyclable paper trays. We are proudly WBENC certified and our delicious meals are designed to offer high-quality, healthy options for you and your loved ones to enjoy solo or as a feast within minutes.

At House of Kajaana, we believe comfort comes from knowing you have a delicious meal waiting for you, whenever you’re hungry. Creating that comfort and joy for you is what guides everything we do. Our meals can be in found grocery stores and online as we launch in 2023. Thank you to our dream team of investors and advisors! We look forward to sharing our treasures with you for many years to come.

Description: includesign is a Rhode Island product design company that creates products that empower individuals with disabilities. Their products are designed collaboratively with the disability community using the human centered design process and are 100% made in America. inclu’s flagship product is the LapSnap, a patent-pending collapsible carryall for wheelchair users.
Product_Types: The LapSnap is a patent-pending, collapsible carryall designed with and for wheelchair users. the LapSnap consists of a plastic base, a metal frame, and a fabric cover, which act together to hold your belongings. Thanks to the versatile strap, you can attach the LapSnap directly to yourself of your wheelchair in a variety of comfortable ways, leaving your hands free to maneuver your chair and go about your daily tasks.

Description: Hartfiel Medical distributes hard case nasal cannula prong covers and fleece nasal cannula oxygen tubing covers. Our award-winning signature O2 FRESH brand nasal cannula prong cover stores and keeps clean nasal cannula prongs and enables the user to hang oxygen tubing out of the way and declutter the patient bedside of a trip hazard during oxygen therapy. It is a sustainable replacement for using plastic bags to store nasal cannulas and is faster and easier to use, ventilated, and sanitizable and reusable. Our customers use them as a patient comfort and convenience item as a cash charge to residents and patients or absorbed into the facilities room charge. It is also available as a promotional item with facility name for welcome packets, senior living tour thank you gifts, and discharge item as well. It is reusable and sanitizable and made of FDA approved materials. Our soft fleece nasal cannula oxygen tubing covers reduce the discomfort of oxygen tubing across the face and behind the ears and are machine washable. Both items are made in the USA.
Product_Types:
Nasal cannula prong cover
Nasal cannula oxygen tubing fleece cover

Name: JAB MiXOLOGY
Description:
JAB MiXOLOGY takes the guesswork out of handcrafted cocktails at home. With these products, you have everything to make a unique flavor experience and all you need to do is add your favorite spirit.

Simply pour the ingredients into your 16oz JAB Jar and fill. In just two hours, you will have a beautifully aromatic, flavored spirit that can be served on the rocks or topped with your favorite mixer. 

Alcohol isn’t necessary to enjoy the JAB flavor experience. The canisters of the two tea blends also can brew one gallon of light and delicious teas. Or try the two spicy Bloody Mary blends as spice mixes or rubs in culinary applications.

Tea
Infusion Bar Tool Kit

Insect protein requires less land, water and emits almost no greenhouse gases.

It’s also the healthy choice - a complete protein and it also has fiber, iron, vitamin B2 & 12 and the list goes on and on.  It really is a superfood!!  

Jiminy’s products nourish your pet & promote long-term stewardship of the earth - fighting climate change with no compromises!

Through our crafts, girls have the opportunity to learn the stories of these remarkable women and create a tangible keepsake to remind them to be a trailblazer and not a spectator.
Product_Types:
LeadHER Craft Kits:
WINNER: Good Housekeeping 2022 Best Toys Award
Our LeadHER™ collection introduces pre-teen girls ages, 7-12, to mighty trailblazing women like Frida Kahlo, Maya Angelou, Amelia Earhart, and Rosa Parks, while creating a lasting, year-round, keepsake that can be displayed proudly in their room.

Our craft kits:
- provide an educational story – each kit tells the story of a wise leader, providing the opportunity for girls to learn how to step into their power.
- challenge girls to think like LeadHERs – our kits include thoughtful discussion questions that encourage girls to chase their dreams and use their voice for change.
- give back – for every purchase made, we donate a portion of the proceeds to organizations working to empower girls across the globe.
- are inspiring - Through learning about our mighty women, girls get the chance to see themselves in their stories and know they are capable of anything.

InnovateHER Craft Kits:
Let's show our girls how to be entrepreneurs! 

Our modern InnovateHER craft kits are designed to spark your girl's creativity while creating an opportunity for her to earn some extra spending money while creating her own business. This collection is perfect to jumpstart their first business. Each craft kit
features everything she’ll need to construct, package, and sell the handmade crafts she creates. 

We also include a Mighty Girl Biz Plan (think of it as a business plan for pre-teens) to get her thinking like a boss. Because lemonade stands are so last century!

Name: La Fourmi Bionique Inc.
Description: Fourmi Bionique granolas were born from a passion for exceptional ingredients and the hard work of Geneviève Gagnon, an entrepreneur, creator, and food lover at heart. The name primarily reflects the meticulous work put forth by Geneviève to create these cereal blends since 2004. It also reflects the desire to offer an alternative within the current food industry: healthy, high-quality artisanal granola while maintaining a solid connection with local producers in organic and fair-trade agriculture. This company has been awarded many prestigious prizes since its inception, driving it to innovate every day, without ever compromising on the quality of their granolas.
Product_Types: Honey & maple syrup roasted granolas, heathy muesli & oatmeal, gluten free & grain free granolas and, gluten free sulfite free snacks.
Where: Sold in Quebec supermarket stores or online, at www.lafourmibionique.com. Some products are on amazon.ca and costco.ca

Description:
Lift Your Table® folding table risers – is an ergonomic safety product that raises the height of folding tables to multiple heights without tools.

Is your back killing you?

In the U.S., workplace back pain is the biggest cause of lost productivity, missed workdays, and worker’s compensation claims. Many workers suffer from back pain due to improper ergonomics of their work environment, including those who work from folding tables in a standing capacity.

Many notable companies use our risers for worker safety in their offices, retail floors, and warehouses including: Whole Foods, Netflix, Pepsi, Nordstrom, Stanford University, Lululemon, Holiday Inn Express, Goodwill, and The North Face.

During the global pandemic, businesses used our risers to raise sanitation tables and to improve social distancing barriers. 

Our risers also appeal to consumers who use them when crafting, sewing, grooming, doing trade shows, cooking, demonstrating, gift wrapping, folding and more.  

Lift Your Table® is fast becoming a staple in every work, office, and school environment and will soon be as commonplace … as the folding table itself!

Lift Your Table®...Save Your Back!

Lift Your Table folding table risers - Counter Height, Original Foot

Name: Lightning Nuggets, Inc
Description:
Lightning Nuggets, Inc. Manufactures renewable non-toxic all natural fire starters. Our company has the philosophy to offer only a product of environmental enhancements and consumer satisfactions.  For this reason, we use recycled forest by-products within our lumber industry, and only a completely purified, recycled, food grade quality paraffin wax. Our product has no hazards and completes nature's carbon cycle as a renewable resource.

The Lightning Nugget, our original firestarter, when placed round side down and lighting the top flat edge, is guaranteed to burn for at least 15 minutes, reaching 480 degrees with an 8+ inch flame.

The Lightnin' Bug was originally designed for use in pellet stoves. It is about a 1/3 the size of a Nugget. When placed curved side down and lighting the top flat edge, is guaranteed to burn for at least 7 minutes, reaching 360 degrees with a 4+ inch flame.

Lightning Nuggets, Inc. products are non-toxic, environmentally safe firestarters that have been made right here in the U.S.A. since 1978!
Product_Types: Lightning Nuggets, Lil Nugget, and Lightnin' Bugs

Name: Medebra
Description:
Medebra offers post surgical Bras and Mastectomy Kits. Considered to be durable medical equipment, the collection includes the only patented, reimbursable, multi-purpose and multi-gender bras and vests. Founded by a breast cancer survivor, Medebra is on a mission to make a long over due humanitarian change in patient care. Products can be used from the day of biopsy or treatments and later as great exercise or sleep bras.

Medebra is more comfortable to wear than previous port surgery devices and at the same time lets you comfortably choose correct sizes.

Description: Based in San Francisco, munchrooms is dedicated to making healthier snacking more achievable and sustainable with our meat-alternative jerky. Our handcrafted jerky has the subtle umami of mushrooms, the flavor of freshly ground spices, and a meaty, satisfying texture. We want to provide people more plant-based meat alternatives that are good for the body and the planet. Through our Asian inspired flavors, we hope to expand people’s cultural palates and bring people together through our mutual love for snacking.

Description:
In Greek, the words Eu-Genia (you-geh-knee-ah) mean the origin of goodness, which says it all about the woman for whom the brand was named (the mother of this mother/daughter-team). Founded by Naa-Sakle Akuete and named after her mom, Eugenia, Eu’Genia Shea provides consumers with clean moisturizers from tree to shelf. 

Number one is always shea butter, followed by four other plant-based ingredients: shea oil, grapefruit or lavender essential oils, moringa oil, and baobab oil. This makes it highly efficient for daily moisturizing as well as reducing the appearance of scarring, eczema, psoriasis, and stretch marks.
Product_Types: Dermatological Strength, Everyday Strength, Pregnancy Strength
Values: Cruelty Free,Ethically Made,Vegan,Women of Color,Allergen-Friendly,Fair Trade,Organic,Green/Sustainability,Giving Back

They’re naturally grain-, dairy- , soy-, and refined sugar-free and certified Gluten Free and Non-GMO. They are a great grab-n-go snack for the whole family available direct online, in select local and natural grocers, and in qualified meal and snack kits.

Name: Numa Foods
Description:
Numa means daughter (nu) and mother (ma) in Chinese. Numa snacks honor the timeless tradition of a mother's cooking and pay homage to Asian roots all the while keeping the modern, on-the-go consumer in mind. 
Their flagship product re-imagines the popular Asian nougat without any artificial ingredients and excessive sugar. By using only six natural, functional ingredients, they have created a candy that contains 40% less sugar than the standard candy bar, four grams of protein per serving and more than ten essential vitamins. It is truly a better-for-you nougat that still retains the famously creamy and chewy texture of classic Asian nougat.

Name: O'MY!
Description:
O’MY Dairy Free Gelato, is a women-owned small business located in Richmond, VA that crafts deliciously creamy, simply made gelato with really real ingredients. In 2017 Co-founders Allison Monette and Julie Bishop knew that better was possible and set out to create a creamy, allergy-friendly treat that would be free of artificial colors, flavors, and made with natural, plant-based ingredients sourced with care. Today O’MY offers six flavors that are classically sweetened with cane sugar and four flavors that are Keto-Friendly, with 1-2 grams of sugars per serving. 

All O’MY gelatos are Non-GMO Project Verified, Certified Plant Based, vegan and free from milk, gluten/wheat, tree nuts, peanuts, eggs, soy, sesame, and pea protein.  Time to Believe in Better Dairy Free.
Product_Types: Dairy Free Gelato

Description: OMG! Pretzels is a women-owned, family-run company that specializes in creating the perfect sensory snacking experience that every snack lover dreams about!  With a wide range of bold, mouthwatering flavors and our iconic, crave-worthy crunch, their gourmet seasoned sourdough nuggets are guaranteed to make you a true believer in love at first bite. Once you pop one in your mouth, OMG! comes popping out!
Product_Types:
Garlic OMG! Pretzels: The flagship OMG! Pretzels flavor, our Garlic Pretzels started it all! Their delectable taste and the perfect blend of savory garlic and fresh herbs will have you saying, “OMG!” with every single bite. These crunchy, gourmet flavored pretzel wonders make the perfect stand-alone snack, and are an elegant and delicious addition to cheese platters, soups, and salads.

Sweet & Salty OMG! Pretzels: The classic combination of cinnamon and raw cane sugar are the stars of our Sweet & Salty Pretzels. But, don’t worry, you will get the perfect touch of salt as well to round out this amazingly poppable flavor. Whoever said you can’t have the best of both worlds, never tried our Sweet & Salty Pretzels!

Lemon Pepper OMG! Pretzels: When life gives us lemons, we make our zesty and zingy Lemon Pepper Pretzels. Every bite of these scrumptious and tangy sourdough pretzels has a sweet and peppery goodness to remind you of sunshine and summertime. For all of our lemon pepper fans: these are for YOU!

Salty Butterscotch OMG! Pretzels: Dessert time, meet snacktime! Our delectable Salty Butterscotch pretzels are the perfect solution to your sweet tooth cravings, leaving a lasting creamy taste on the tip of your tongue! Tastes just like the savory candies that Grandma would share!

Name: Once Again Home Co.
Description:
We’re here to help you ease the transition into eco-friendly living and offer a tangible way for individual consumers to make a difference. We strive to offer versatile, durable and stylish products for your home and everyday living. Whether you’re replacing kitchen towels, adding pretty hand towels to the bathroom or delivering a thoughtful housewarming gift, we hope you’re inspired to take steps towards other good habits.
Our towels are made with post-consumer materials (bottles) while also allowing us to use less water in their production. The result is a highly absorbent (that’s the combination of recycled material and polyamide) that is also quick dry. This unique fabrication is perfect to replace paper products in your home as well – say goodbye to paper towels and paper napkins. 
We are here to create positive planetary habits.
Product_Types: Our Multi-Purpose Towels in different Sizes: Anywhere Towel, Biggie Towel, Mini Towel.

Description:
Sisters and farmers Stephanie and Hayley Painter launched Painterland Sisters Organic Skyr Yogurt as part of their mission to preserve, showcase and utilize their family’s Pennsylvania organic dairy farm, Painterland Farms.

Painterland Sisters offers healthy, honest and sustainable products that connect consumers to the direct source of their food: the American farmer. Their fourth-generation family-owned and operated farm practices regenerative farming and rotationally graze their cattle on fresh pastures to keep the soil as nutrient-rich as possible.

Painterland Sisters Organic Skyr Yogurt contains billions of probiotics (BB12), is high in protein and calcium, lactose-free and lower in sugar. Painterland Sisters is farmer-owned and certified Woman-Owned Business.
Product_Types: We offer 6 flavors of our skyr: Savannah’s Peach, Meadow Berry, Strawberry, Blueberry Lemon, Vanilla and Plain.

Name: Plantlife
Description:
The focus at Plantlife is manufacturing the cleanest, plant-based body care products on the market. Since 1994, they've used "old world" formulas combined with the timeless sciences of herbology and aromatherapy to create the perfect blend of science and nature. 

Plantlife manufactures all natural, aromatherapy products that are good for you! They use fresh organic herbs, 100% pure essential oil, raw plant oils and other natural ingredients that feed your skin and restore your body. Each of their aromatherapy creations is prepared with the intent of enriching your life as well as not harming the environment.

Name: Pretty Pokets
Description:
Pretty Pokets designs uniquely stylish diaper bags, laptop bags, backpacks, and totes for women on the go. Pretty Pokets is designed to find harmony between usefulness, commonsense and fashion. They have multiple categories of bags and accessories and all them exist for a reason - to serve one and only one powerhouse: "The Women of Today and The Women on the Go." 

The company was founded by Madhu Challa, a hardware engineer who designed a unique diaper bag that features both a diaper and trash bag dispenser, making on-the-go diaper changes a breeze. At Pretty Pokets, it’s her mission to add incredible value to women’s lives by designing and creating intentional products that find harmony between usefulness, common sense, and fashion.
Product_Types:
Diaper Bags
Laptop Bags
Purses
Wristlet Wallets

Their mission is to create exceptional experiences enhancing everyday foods by introducing people to bold flavors they can feel confident using. 

Our founder is a food lover and mom of food allergy children. She was sick and tired of spending hours scrutinizing food labels wondering what was in her spices and sauces. Each product was carefully curated with her family in mind. She wanted to expose her children to all the flavors she grew up with and wanted a safe way to do that.

Food is a source of connection, and we are honored to be at the table.

Name: Sauce Goddess
Description:
The Sauce Goddess Story

We’ve never done ordinary. We dare to be different by being very basic in our approach to food.

Originally, Sauce Goddess was inspired by a loving, hand-crafted, sauce recipe secretly passed down from father Keith to daughter Jennifer. We took that great recipe and made it better.

We’re very proud of everything we put in our products and purposeful in everything we leave out. We are making real food using real food ingredients.

Our award-winning sauces, spices and new dip mixes are deliciously different from anything else in their categories. We have done it all-natural, vegan, certified gluten free, and free from ANY additives or preservatives. We have been doing it that way for almost 20 years.

We are a woman-owned business, and deeply devoted community member. We partner with local and national organizations like Partnerships with Industry and other organizations across the country – helping challenged adults with disabilities perform jobs that are specific to their special skill set.

Our flavors are so good, we say “if you don’t lick your fingers, someone else will!”

Description:
Originally, Sauce Goddess was inspired by a family sauce recipe passed down from father Keith to daughter Jennifer. 

After over 20 years in business, the current Sauce Goddess obscenely delicious food creations are anything but ordinary. 
      
Real food with real ingredients made by real folks. You won’t find any additives or preservatives. Their award-winning flavors are so powerful because they come from the real stuff. 

Everything they make is Vegan, Certified Gluten-Free, Non-GMO. 
        
Sauce Goddess gives back by hiring specially gifted adults to perform jobs that are suited to their special skill set. Providing fun, purpose and joy in their lives.
       
People gathering together and enjoying a great meal together is what it’s all about. Creating smiles with food. 

And yes Sauce Goddess flavors are so good they say “if you don’t lick your fingers, someone else will!”

Description:
Señor Rio Tequila, an ultra-premium all-natural small batch brand was founded in 2009. Their tequila is made in the lowlands of Jalisco, in the town of Tequila, MX with a process dates back three generations in the founder, Debbie Medina Gach's, family and honors her father nicknamed Señor Rio. It is 100% blue weber agave harvested from a single estate and has been growing organically on taste and presentation. 

With every bottle sold $1.00 is donated to WeCareCrusade,org a foundation on a mission to help families with children who have special needs dedicated to Debbie Medina Gach's twin granddaughters.

Description:
The tray organizers will surely add a feeling of calm, when you slip it on.  Imagine a typical overcrowded flight and being stuffed in that ever shrinking area around your seat. Using the Serenity organizer creates a sense of calm by providing easily accessible clean pockets for your water bottle, computer, headphones etc. when the tray is up . When you lower your tray, you will have a clean surface to work on and enjoy your refreshments on. If you are traveling with kids, give them their own organizers so they can easily manage their own stuff.  When you are getting ready to disembark, voila, the tray organizer becomes a drawstring tote to store your belongings and toss in your carry-on.  Nothing gets left behind!
 
The seat organizers also create a protective barrier between you and your seat/headrest while also providing much needed storage for your necessities. Particularly helpful when you are seated in a bulkhead seat.
Product_Types: Tray Organizers & Seat Organizers for travel

Name: Spinster Sisters Co.
Description:
Spinster Sisters Co., is a B Corp certified personal care company in Golden, Colorado. They believe that doing right matters and are on a mission to be plastic-free and make the best personal care products for you and our planet.

Kelly Perkins, Founder + CEO, started making soap and skincare in the '90s with a simple goal: avoiding toxic ingredients. She was horrified to learn about chemicals like Triclosan, an antibacterial agent that is a hormone inhibitor. Finding brands that were truly clean was hard, so she learned to make her own plant-based soap and skincare. People fell in love with her products and from there Spinster Sisters was born.

Description: Spirit Sox USA specializes in high-quality, fun, and creative socks. Over the past 7 years we have perfected the custom sock process and now have a sock shop that contains seasonal limited edition socks you can snag for yourself or gift to someone else! Description:
Sugar Bliss is a woman minority-owned bakery in downtown Chicago. Sugar Bliss offers a wide variety of baked goods including morning pastries, cupcakes, cake pops, French macarons, brownies, cookies, and more. Sugar Bliss bakes everything on-site and from scratch using only the highest quality, natural ingredients, such as European Cocoa, Nielsen Massey vanilla, and real fruits. Sugar Bliss provides catering to corporate events, office meetings, and a variety of celebrations including birthdays, retirement, weddings, and bridal and baby showers.

Sugar Bliss also has 4 varieties of packaged cookies in 5 oz bags sold at retailers - Sea Salt Chocolate Chunk, Rainbow Sugar, Gluten Free Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip, and the OMG cookie which has potato chips, pretzels, cap’n crunch cereal, chocolate chips, oats, and a hint of coffee. Their social mission is to create a blissful world for all and donate a portion of the proceeds to support women and minority entrepreneurs, wildlife conservation, and use recyclable packaging.

Name: Sugarbird Sweets and Teas
Description:
Sugarbird Sweets is a handcrafted scone and tea company founded in 2009 by music video producer turned baker Kei Okumura. Okumura is passionate about afternoon tea - not just as a time to enjoy tea and sweets, but as a moment to reset and reconnect in the middle of the day. After she was classically trained as a chef in Paris, she worked to perfect the humble scone and created an expansive scone menu with supremely delicious flavors including strawberry buttermilk, matcha white chocolate, feta chive,
black sesame white chocolate, and ube coconut, as well as wheat-free and plant-based options.

Sugarbird Sweets also offers a selection of fine teas, frozen scone dough, an assortment of baked treats, and carefully curated gift boxes. The bakery ships nationwide, so customers can host their own afternoon teas and experiences around the country.

Name: Teffola
Description:
Teffola makes artisan granola celebrating ancient grains. Their star ingredient, teff, is grown and processed on their 7th generation family farm where they are pivoting from corn and soybeans to alternative grains and seeds. Teffola, teff granola, has a low sugar content so other flavors from plant based ingredients are able to shine through. All flavors are at or less than 4 grams of sugar per serving. Shop on their website.

Name: Tempagenix
Description: Temp-N-Toss Disposable Forehead Thermometer Strips are the fast, easy, and eco-friendly way to check for a fever or monitor temperatures for children and adults! Temp-N-Toss thermometer strips are specially designed to give a quick, accurate reading, and the medical-grade adhesive means they'll stay in place for continual monitoring for up to 48 hours. Plus, the non-invasive forehead strips are ideal for checking the temperature of a fussy toddler, sleeping infant or cranky child. Each all-paper thermometer is free of latex, mylar, glass, mercury and other harmful chemicals, and they do not require batteries. Temp-N-Toss Disposable Forehead Thermometer Strips are also perfect for travel; just slip them in a pocket, purse, or diaper bag so you can always have them on hand.

Name: TETON Sports
Description:
TETON Sports began as an idea. An idea that no matter the person, no matter the time and no matter the place, anyone and everyone should be able to get outdoors and enjoy life. They started small and grew, determined to build a world and a culture and gear that would allow them all to experience the beauty and magic of the outdoors. Their tents, sleeping bags, cots, hammocks, and backpacks do just that.

They are a privately held company, incorporated in Utah in 2005. They are headquartered at the foot of the Wasatch Mountains in Cedar Hills, Utah, with a showroom and warehouse in Salt Lake City. Visit them and the mountains they love.

Name: The Austin Red Tent Experience, dba Jeany's Caribbean Elixirs
Description:
Jeany's Caribbean Elixirs is a premium Caribbean-inspired cold-pressed juice brand, focusing on functional ingredients. We started our brand in 2017, searching for fruit juices that reminded us of our grandmother's juice recipes from Grenada. Mama Lyris, our maternal grandmother, was the OG Master Herbalist in our family. Mama was self-taught and intuitively knew which fruits, vegetables and herbs to combine together to create healing for our family and her community. Needless to say, we did not find anything in the marketplace that stood up to her handmade elixirs. What we did find were tropical juices that were heat pasteurized, used syrups and powders, and tasted watered-down.   

The solution is Jeany's Caribbean Elixirs! Our elixirs feature clean labels with simple, functional ingredients focusing on anti-inflammation, are available without added sweeteners, are cold-pressed and have been used for chronic health issues such as high blood pressure, chronic joint pain and digestion issues.   

We seek to honor our grandmother's legacy as a master herbalist and community organizer by hiring those from marginalized communities, such as foster youth, single parents and returning citizens (i.e., post incarceration) and giving them a livable wage. We are proud to be a second-chance employer.
Product_Types:
Premium Caribbean-inspired cold-pressed juices:
Mama’s Ginger (ginger, pineapple, lime)
Berry Breeze (strawberry, mango, ginger, pineapple, lime)
Caribe Azul - (blue spirulina, lime, pineapple, apple)
(SEASONAL - MAY through SEPTEMBER) - Floral Sunset - strawberry, watermelon, infused with lavender
Where:
Manana Coffeehouse
The Driskill Hotel
Whole Foods Market (Austin TX) - launching 04/2023

Description: The Chai Box, founded by Monica Sunny in Atlanta, Georgia, is a small-batch Chai company bringing the traditional craft of chai making to everyone’s home. The Chai Box specializes in Chai concentrate, unique loose-leaf Chai blends inspired by different regions in India, and spices. They source single-origin spices from family-owned farms in India and have a focus on sustainability.  What started in Monica’s kitchen in 2016 as a way to teach her boys how to make traditional Chai, became one of Oprah's Favorite Things in 2021! The Chai Box crafts premium Chai that honors their culture and heritage.
Product_Types: Chai Concentrate, All Chai'd Up (Loose Leaf Masala Chai), Hill Station (Loose-Leaf Masala Chai), Hill Station (Loose Leaf Rose & Cardamom Chai) and Best Seller's Gift Set (3 Loose-Leaf Chai Options + a Stainless Steel Steeper in a Gift Box)

Description: VegaJelly was launched in 2022. Their founder, Beth Kloos, couldn’t find anything that would give her the flawless skin that she remembered her mother always having. She also didn’t want any harmful chemicals in her beauty products. She created VegaJelly, which is 100% all-natural plant-based moisturizer. It has the consistency of petroleum jelly but is made from 100% vegetable oil. Simply put, it’s vegetable jelly — hence the name VegaJelly.

Description: Family-owned and operated since 1967, ECOS makes plant-powered laundry detergents and cleaners that are safer for people, pets, and the planet. ECOS products are made sustainably in the USA using global ingredients without dyes, 1,4-dioxane, parabens, phthalates, or optical brighteners. A WBENC-Certified Women’s Business Enterprise and Black-owned company, ECOS is Climate Positive and restores 110% of its carbon, water, and energy use back to the earth. ECOS, ECOS for Pets, and ECOS PRO cleaners are available at major club and grocery retailers and natural foods stores throughout the U.S., internationally, and online. For more information and retail locations, visit ecos.com.
Product_Types:
Hypoallergenic Laundry Detergent – Free & Clear
Enjoy plant-powered cleaning without added dyes or fragrances. Our powerful hypoallergenic laundry detergent uses a coconut-derived cleaner to break down odors and eliminate stubborn stains. Our detergent formula is readily biodegradable, gentle on sensitive skin, and safe for use with septic systems or greywater tanks.
 
Laundry Detergent Packs – Free & Clear
Laundry without the plastic bottle! ECOS Laundry Detergent Packs are a sustainable and convenient all-in-one laundry solution. Skip the drippy mess and measuring of traditional liquid laundry detergent – simply drop in one pack per load.
 
Laundry Detergent Sheets – Magnolia & Lily
Say hello to the future of laundry! With plant-derived cleaning agents combined with the sweet floral scents of magnolia and lily, our laundry detergent sheets are tough on stains and odors – without all the mess of liquid laundry soaps and plastic bottles. Our eco-conscious laundry detergent sheets are lightweight, featuring plastic-free packaging and a readily biodegradable formula.
 
Dish Soap – Grapefruit
Our dish soap has safer ingredients for a cleaner kitchen. Infused with the invigorating scent of grapefruit, our formula uses cleaners derived from coconuts to provide a gentle, effective, plant-powered clean. Get rid of grease and food residue without drying out your skin.

Description: VITAVATE™ is a premium, trustworthy dietary supplement brand intentionally designed to support heart health, energy, and focus on-the-go! Our mantra, “Fill Your Cup First", communicates our desire for VITAVATE to be an integral part of your daily routine. More importantly, “Fill Your Cup First” recognizes the importance of prioritizing self-care amid competing responsibilities.
Product_Types:
VITAVATE™ ENERGY
- SUSTAIN ENERGY WITHOUT THE CRASH- Fill your cup first with our naturally flavored strawberry powdered dietary supplements to elevate and sustain energy levels during the day without a crash. 
- CLEAN, NATURAL, PREMIUM, INGREDIENTS- The all-natural blend of vitamins and minerals includes green tea, ginseng, choline, ginger root, grape seed extracts, PABA, and Resveratrol. 
- EASY TO CONSUME & HYDRATE - Experiencing pill fatigue? Pour one packet of the powdered mix into 8-16 oz water. Shake or stir and drink up! Best served over ice. The delicious strawberry flavoring will make it much easier to hydrate during your day. 
- ENERGY ON THE GO - Each pouch has 15 individually sealed packets (6g) that you can easily fit into your pocket, wallet, purse, you name it! 
- QUALITY ASSURANCE - VITAVATE products are manufactured in a cGMP-approved facility. Every ingredient and production lot is tested to ensure the highest standards of efficacy and food safety.

VITAVATE™ FOCUS 
- FOCUS AND MIND CLARITY- Fill your cup first with our refreshing, naturally flavored orange dietary powdered supplement to elevate overall cognitive function. 
- CLEAN, NATURAL, PREMIUM, INGREDIENTS- The all-natural blend of vitamins and minerals include Vitamin B6, Vitamin A, Vitamin E, Choline, and Fiber. 
- EASY TO CONSUME & HYDRATE - Experiencing pill fatigue? Pour one packet of the powdered mix into 8-16 oz water. Shake or stir and drink up! Best served over ice. The delicious orange flavoring will make it much easier to hydrate during your day. 
- FOCUS ON THE GO - Each pouch has 15 individually sealed packets (6g) that you can easily fit into your pocket, wallet, purse, you name it! 
- QUALITY ASSURANCE - VITAVATE products are manufactured in a cGMP-approved facility. Every ingredient and production lot is tested to ensure the highest efficacy and food safety standards.

VITAVATE™ HEART
- HEART - Fill your cup first with our refreshing, naturally flavored lemon powdered dietary supplement to support heart health. 
- CLEAN, NATURAL, PREMIUM, INGREDIENTS- the all-natural blend of vitamins and minerals includes Vitamin B6, Vitamin E, Magnesium, Selenium, Calcium, Taurine, and Fiber. 
- EASY TO CONSUME- Experiencing pill fatigue? Pour one packet of the powdered mix into 8-16 oz of water. Stir or shake and drink up! Best served over ice. 
- HYDRATION ON THE GO- Each pouch contains 15 individually sealed packets (7g) that you can easily fit into your pocket, wallet, or purse; you name it! The lemon flavoring will make it much easier to stay hydrated during your day. 
- QUALITY ASSURANCE - VITAVATE products are manufactured in a cGMP-approved facility. Each production lot is tested to ensure efficacy and food safety standards are met.

Description: YANY Beauty transcends being merely a brand or cosmetics store; it epitomizes a comprehensive beauty and wellness encounter. Visitors are welcomed to this premier destination, offering avant-garde, clean beauty crafted in-house and globally sourced from inventive indie founders. The brand's pride lies in formulating vegan/vegetarian, cruelty-free products, ensuring alignment with ethical values. Their tech-enabled retail approach seamlessly merges luxury, inclusivity, and sustainability, fashioning a distinctive beauty and wellness experience in both physical and virtual realms. YANY Beauty, originating as a 2012 hobby, has evolved into a global beauty phenomenon, surpassing conventional boundaries. Embracing individual beauty, their commitment to diversity propels the creation of inclusive beauty products and services, emphasizing representation for all skin types, tones, and ages. Sustainability is a key focus, with a conscious effort to minimize environmental impact. As a Black-owned, woman-led, family-operated business, YANY Beauty fosters a community that values diversity, celebrating differences. WBENC women-owned and Leaping Bunny certified, the brand is dedicated to redefining the beauty industry through inclusive and sustainable practices.

Description: Yellowcake Shop Clothing is a brand of sustainable fashion, crafting handmade contemporary women's apparel that seamlessly blends modernity with timeless elegance. Devoted to responsible design, the founder personally creates patterns and prototypes, ensuring each piece is a masterpiece. Collaborating with a local team of home-based stitchers, the brand embraces a small batch production model, minimizing waste and utilizing dead stock. Committed to environmental consciousness, Yellowcake Shop encourages clients to exchange well-loved garments for credits, resells preloved items, and champions upcycling. The brand's mission extends beyond style, promoting a healthier planet while offering professional women enduring, versatile wardrobe staples that stand the test of time.

Description:
ZenOsa Organics creates natural children's health products formulated using science-backed organic ingredients. Each formula is created by pediatrician moms using the ingredients they would choose for their children and patients. 

The first two products to launch are research-backed natural cough remedies and immune boosters. Their baby cough syrup is the only one on the market to feature monk fruit as a tasty natural sweetener versus agave used by most competitors, which is high in sugar. For children over the age of one year, their organic children's cough syrup uses organic honey, which has been shown to soothe coughs and scratchy throats. Both products also include science-backed immune boosters; organic elderberry, zinc, vitamin C, and vitamin D.

Description:
ZenToes was started by Sarah Parks after one of her family members struggled to find bunion care products that were affordable and actually worked.

After testing dozens of products, Zentoes settled on the best few and began selling online. Bunion sufferers around the country found their products and loved them just as much as they did. Since then, the product line has grown and is now recommended by podiatrists, physical therapists, chiropractors, and more. All of Zentoes products are still rigorously tested on their own feet before they’re approved to be sold on ZenToes.com.

Zentoes is a small, woman-owned, FDA Registered business based in Bellingham, WA. The products at ZenToes provide holistic, fast pain relief for foot, bunion, ankle, metatarsalgia, plantar fasciitis, hand, and other types of pain. The products are designed to relieve pain without embarrassment or surgery, and bright, colorful packaging is used to normalize foot conditions that are the most common such as bunions, hammertoes, corns and calluses, lace bite, strains and sprains, and more.

Zentoes is passionate about living a healthy, active lifestyle and believe that no one should have to slow down due to foot pain. Many of their products are made from reusable, latex-free gel that is sanitary and easy to clean with soap and warm water. Most of their products are designed to be worn on either the right or left foot to meet your needs and they are comfortable and easy to use. Zentoes is here to help you live a pain-free, balanced lifestyle no matter your age.
Product_Types:
1. Single Loop Toe Spacer for Bunion Pain
2. Metatarsal Sleeves with Gel Pads
3. Gel Toe Caps
4. Buddy Wraps for Broken Toes
